        "summary": "Broccoli Rice Dish takes around <b>45 minutes</b> from beginning to end. This recipe serves 1 and costs $2.89 per serving. This main course has <b>1127 calories</b>, <b>20g of protein</b>, and <b>68g of fat</b> per serving. This recipe from Foodista has 1 fans. If you have broccoli, milk, cheez whiz, and a few other ingredients on hand, you can make it. It is a good option if you're following a <b>gluten free</b> diet. Taking all factors into account, this recipe <b>earns a spoonacular score of 57%</b>, which is solid. Try <a href=\"https://spoonacular.com/recipes/broccoli-rice-hot-dish-107489\">Broccoli Rice Hot Dish</a>, <a href=\"https://spoonacular.com/recipes/chicken-asparagus-broccoli-wild-rice-cheese-dish-111251\">Chicken, Asparagus, Broccoli, Wild Rice, & Cheese Dish</a>, and <a href=\"https://spoonacular.com/recipes/one-dish-broccoli-rotini-410753\">One Dish Broccoli Rotini</a> for similar recipes.",
